title: Heed the Warnings
description:
A new moon coincides with fresh starts and rebirth. But a full moon can leave an opening for evil to find its way into our lives. If you don't listen to those who warn you, then you may end up facing fire consequences.

First, mother ‘nature’ knows best
Followed by new friends come with killer baggage 
Then, don’t ignore the signs 
Finally in our featured story, a new house isn't always an empty house.
